      <title>欧元区经济摇摇欲坠 市场押注欧洲央行将加快降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/euro-zone-s-teetering-economy-fuels-bets-on-faster-ecb-rate-cuts</link>
